thread.title: Ellen Rayburn
thread.title_full: Hole-In-One Trophies reviewed by Ellen Rayburn

author: Ellen Rayburn
title: Ellen Rayburn
text: I ordered a hole-in-one plaque about a week before Christmas and I was amazed at how soon it got to my house! It was perfectly packaged and protected and the outcome was beautiful! They got the spelling and everything right, but hopefully a misspelling would never be an issue on their end! I got continuous emails letting my know when my order was shipped and tracking information! It always makes me feel good when I know the tracking information about my package! The site is super user friendly and self explanatory! (If you know your golf, that is). I will definitely be ordering from them again!
